{{ja-kanjitab|yomi=k|ころも}}

From {{inh|ja|ojp|sort=ころも|-}}. Appears in the ''{{w|Kojiki}}'' completed in 712 CE.

Ultimate derivation unclear. May be a compound of {{compound|ja|sort=ころも|ころ|tr1=koro|pos1=uncertain meaning, possibly “wrapping”, cognate with {{m|ja|転|tr=koro||roller; rolling}}|裳|tr2=mo|t2=lower robe}}.

{{ja-noun|ころも}}

# {{lb|ja|sort=ころも|archaic}} [[clothes]], [[clothing]]
# a [[robe]] {{gloss|as worn by a monk, nun, or priest}}
# a [[coating]] on an item of [[food]], such as [[batter]] or [[icing]]
# the [[outer]] [[shell]] or [[carapace]] of an [[insect]] or other [[arthropod]]
# the [[hide]] or [[feathers]] of a small [[animal]]

* {{sense|clothing}} {{ja-r|服|ふく}}, {{ja-r|衣%服|い%ふく}}
* {{sense|robe}} {{ja-r|着%物|き%もの}} {{qualifier|non-clerical}}; {{ja-r|法%衣|ほう%い}} {{qualifier|clerical}}, {{ja-r|僧%衣|そう%い}} {{qualifier|clerical}}
* {{sense|food coating, insect shell, animal skin}} {{ja-r|外%皮|がい%ひ}}

{{der-top}}
* {{ja-r|衣%替え|ころも%がえ}}: the [[changing]] of one's [[clothes]]
* {{ja-r|衣%虱|ころも%じらみ}}: the [[body louse]] ((''[[Pediculus humanus]]''), ({{taxlink|Pediculus humanus humanus|species|ver=180312}}), ({{taxlink|Pediculus humanus corporis|species|ver=180312}}))
* {{ja-r|衣%手|ころも%で}}: a [[sleeve]]
* {{ja-r|衣%筥|ころも%ばこ}}: a kind of [[clothing]] [[box]] or [[chest]] that has short [[leg]]s
* {{ja-r|衣%偏|ころも%へん}}: the [[clothing]] [[radical]] {{gloss|a graphical portion of a kanji character}}
* {{ja-r|衣%屋|ころも%や}}: a [[store]] selling [[clerical]] [[robe]]s; a person working in such a store
{{der-bottom}}

{{ja-noun|きぬ}}

# [[clothes]], [[clothing]] {{gloss|particularly clothing worn on the top half of the body}}
# an [[overrobe]]
# the [[skin]], [[hide]], or [[shell]] of an animal; the [[bark]], [[rind]], or [[skin]] of a plant

{{der-top}}
* {{ja-r|衣%落|きぬ%おとし}}: a particular moment in a [[noh]] play where a character approaches the bridge and removes an outer robe wrapped around their hips
{{der-bottom}}

{{der-top}}
* {{ja-r|打ち衣|うちぎ}}: [[everyday]] [[clothing]], particularly [[kimono]]
* {{ja-r|産%衣|うぶ%ぎ}}: [[baby]] [[clothes]]; [[swaddling]] [[clothes]]
* {{ja-r|上%衣|うわ%ぎ}}: an [[overrobe]]
{{der-bottom}}

